+# DEX choice
+
+I picked Aerodrome for the Base swap because it is the primary Base-native liquidity hub and is generally the deepest DEX venue on Base. The implementation uses Aerodrome's canonical Base router at `0xcF77a3Ba9A5CA399B7c97c74d54e5b4d9521c0d` and routes USDC to WETH through the volatile USDC/WETH pool.
